 limits on the intensities\nof ultraviolet line emission from C I, C III, Si II, S III, S IV, S VI, and Fe\nIII.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 May 2001 17:58:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-06"}
