he harder power-full SGR\nevent. We predict such a rich X-Ray precursor signals (more numerous then gamma\nones) during Soft Gamma Repeater peak activities; they should be abundant and\nwithin detection threshold by a permanent monitoring SGRs by Beppo-Sax WFC or\nChandra X ray satellites while at peak activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 May 2001 19:05:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 May 2001 12:20:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 18 May 2001 17:43:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-25"}
